org.jbei.ice.lib.entry.sample.model

Class Sample

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jbei.ice.lib.entry.sample.model.Sample
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IDataModel

    @Entity
public class Sample
extends Object
implements IDataModel
    Store Sample information.

    Each sample is a uniquely identified (via UUIDv4) object representing a physical sample. Storage locations are handled by Storage objects.

    Author:
    Timothy Ham, Zinovii Dmytriv
